crystal-ada (unreleased)

crystal-ada (0.1.0)

  * Initial release.

  * Added:
    - xyz2fract  -- convert coordinates to fractional
    - xyz2ortho  -- convert coordinates to Cartesian
    - xyzformat  -- apply formatting to floating pt. numbers
    - xyzpermute -- permute axes and coordinates

  * Implemented:
    - Processing of the LATTICE and CELL keywords in the XYZ file
      comments
